{"tid":1532943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］可唔可以冷靜啲聽我講 放低所有野","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:44:45.000Z","uid":175326,"like":13,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9420e4ad57715b35c14eda7a3ed003c75c920b58","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"第一，呢幾日，已經睇到黑警佈晒陣咁，不斷加速佢哋嘅行動，已經有好多個手足畀人拉咗，最終只會趨向黑警同政府想要嘅結局。<br />\n<br />\n第二，所有手足千萬唔好再單走或者唔跟大隊走，咁樣只會一個一個畀人拉，手足不斷咁減少。<br />\n<br />\n第三，我哋呢幾日嘅行動，真係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好好好失敗</span></strong>，論成效只係變咗一個造勢大會，抑或是喂喂喂集會，對政府一啲影響到冇。<br />\n<br />\n就以上呢三點，我懇請大家諗清楚，我哋點樣做下一步先可以贏，政府想喺10月1號之前解決我哋，咁我哋係咪應該調轉頭諗下，呢幾個星期都養精蓄銳，到10月1號嘅時候搞壇大野出嚟，而唔係一日一日咁俾人搣人數。"},{"pid":"51d3cc46c0d1e49c173eb632d35fb31e0adb051b","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"3a16b844a0e3ded4868577fd8f7699ec0ac22c87","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"23e5d26eb190a36bb2e798b62f5a69fd162ddfa6","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"9d99e5b01fd0089b4e1841ad2c2a554ec4eff348","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"fd1ce3b3e1acceaeab2afa03a55470e2c8446251","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"bcff8f9f2d52d51e67a725c706db92c8a9dfc674","tid":1532943,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"有point"},{"pid":"e95c2585aaa8522f0ee7a57eac52a87f4223c420","tid":1532943,"uid":175326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"aba1d4d5af4ca559fb69b75c6f01d29fc6bfdd7e","tid":15329